{"tid":2377474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府疑向佐敦禁閉區伊斯蘭教居民派豬肉？","createTime":"2021-01-23T15:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T02:51:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f1bfeb5e47bd11fede8f4a5ea5b051fa9201b48b","tid":2377474,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572014-20210123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572014-20210123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TalEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=d20cb81e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572014-20210123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c4b18971\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572014-20210123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府首度引用規例，清晨4時起圍封佐敦「受限區域」，範圍內的居民午夜前要接受檢測。<br />\n<br />\n由於傳媒在規例生效時身處「受限區域」，亦要接受強制檢測，多間傳媒都登記入住圍封範圍內的賓館。在接受檢測後，圍封範圍內人士都會獲發食物等物資，每袋物資袋各異。有傳媒獲發包括麵包、水果、荳奶、杯麵等可即食物品，亦有提供一盒口罩。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者獲發的物資袋，有5包即食麵、一袋通心粉、4罐罐頭及一盒粟米粒，而賓館未有罐頭刀及煮食工具提供。"},{"pid":"8df243fd459b3bba7c360b5808007f9aa3743e57","tid":2377474,"uid":124,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"南亞自己唔出聲 有咩好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b58b43eda9cac6d5761faab6d76dea0992f1142","tid":2377474,"uid":278168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"正常發揮"},{"pid":"8e13f6d829bb8d323f4559a016ec6a2b3645a1a5","tid":2377474,"uid":335434,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"3b58b43eda9cac6d5761faab6d76dea0992f1142","tid":2377474,"uid":278168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"正常發揮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.nexttv.com.tw/material/news/img